sSink` and `StdoutSink` with single `write_batch_json_resolved` calls\n- Accelerate `first_escape_pos` with SWAR bit tricks (8\u00d7 faster on typical log data)\n- Add fast path in `write_json_string` that avoids allocation when no escaping is needed\n- Replace `format_args!` for control character escaping with a static hex table and `extend_from_slice`","created_at":"2026-04-28T05:59:20Z","updated_at":"2026-04-28T06:22:57Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"6a606cb93c7cb668695eb66455f2f1d4b7413c61","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[{"id":10547812592,"node_id":"LA_kwDORzg8fM8AAAACdLLY8A","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/labels/enhancement","name":"enhancement","color":"a2eeef","default":true,"description":"New feature or request"},{"id":10549918807,"node_id":"LA_kwDORzg8fM8AAAACdNL8Vw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/labels/performance","name":"performance","color":"0E8A16","default":false,"description":"Performance optimization"},{"id":10764332677,"node_id":"LA_kwDORzg8fM8AAAACgZquhQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/labels/size:L","name":"size:L","color":"eb9500","default":false,"description":"This PR changes 100-499 lines, ignoring generated files."},{"id":10808268615,"node_id":"LA_kwDORzg8fM8AAAAChDkXRw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/labels/refactor","name":"refactor","color":"ededed","default":false,"description":null}],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2727/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2727/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/issues/2727/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/statuses/5f51ffb89999e1f72